{
  "stem": "10446.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] one night, the, the group was invited for the opera in Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it so happened that the opera given that night was one that I love and that is never performed in this country.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I wrote to that woman in charge over there and asked if I-- if we could attend.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We would certainly pay for our tickets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she wrote back, you have two tickets free of charge.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You're free to attend all the affairs for the 10 days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Only the hotel rooms are fully booked, and the money allocated for that is completely spoken for.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So, so we wrote back that we have no way and no intention of staying more than for one night, and we would be very grateful if we could attend the, the opera, which we did.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that-- so we were there with the whole group that was invited for that, for those 10 days.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that was quite pleasant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] That was the best memory of Nuremberg after the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We went to where the temple had been.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there's now a big plaque with an inscription.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And at-- on this spot stood the temple, destroyed by the National Socialists in 1938.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And we visited the cemeteries, which are in good condition.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The cemeteries in Germany are maintained by the state, by the individual states, in our case, the state of Bavaria in Munich.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They don't take care of the individual graves, but of the cemetery in, in general.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Did not affect my belief.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It only affected my way of looking at Germans and mankind in particular.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
